sql:
SELECT DISTINCT patient_id, doctor_id 
FROM appointments 
WHERE appointment_date LIKE '2021%';

external_knowledge:
- Blood pressure test results can be an indicator of a patient's cardiovascular health.; 
- The year 2022 refers to the year in which the blood pressure tests were conducted, as specified in the appointment dates.; 
- Highest to lowest order implies arranging the average results from highest to lowest values.

